<lb n="0747b28" ed="T"/>奢<note n="0747011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">博＝摶【明】</note><note n="0747011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">博【大】，摶【明】</note><app n="0747011"><lem wit="【大】">博</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">摶</rdg></app>差<anchor xml:id="fxT13p0747b01"/><note place="inline">八</note><note place="inline">初戒反</note>　蜜羅博差<anchor xml:id="fxT13p0747b02"/><note place="inline">九</note><note place="inline">初戒反</note>　騷剌<note n="0747012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝娑【三】【宮】，＋（婆）【聖】</note><note n="0747012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】，娑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，婆婆【聖】</note><app n="0747012"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】 【宮】">娑</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">婆婆</rdg></app>紇栗帝
